data.description: This is a well taken care of 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with spacious living areas and tranquil bedrooms with walk in closets. This home has newer windows along with a newer furnace and central air conditioning making it great for energy savings. Enjoy gatherings in the generously sized fully fenced in backyard. The back deck is ideal for entertaining or simply unwinding in the fresh air. It also has a large 2 car garage and a shed for additional storage.
